statements: SELECT feedback_id, user_id, rating, feedback_text, product_id FROM user_feedback_ratings;
SELECT * FROM user_feedback_ratings WHERE rating > 4.5;
SELECT feedback_id, user_id, rating FROM user_feedback_ratings WHERE user_id = 101 ORDER BY rating DESC;
SELECT user_id, feedback_text FROM user_feedback_ratings WHERE product_id = 201 AND rating < 3;
SELECT * FROM user_feedback_ratings ORDER BY user_id, rating;
SELECT * FROM user_feedback_ratings WHERE user_id = 100 ORDER BY rating DESC;
SELECT product_id, AVG(rating) AS avg_rating FROM user_feedback_ratings GROUP BY product_id HAVING avg_rating > 4.5 ORDER BY product_id ASC;
SELECT feedback_id, feedback_text FROM user_feedback_ratings WHERE rating BETWEEN 3 AND 4;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(feedback_id) AS total_feedbacks FROM user_feedback_ratings GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_feedbacks > 2;
SELECT product_id, COUNT(feedback_id) AS total_feedbacks, MAX(rating) AS max_rating FROM user_feedback_ratings GROUP BY product_id ORDER BY total_feedbacks DESC, max_rating DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_feedback;
SELECT user_id, rating, comment FROM user_feedback WHERE rating > 3.5;
SELECT user_id, product_id, rating FROM user_feedback ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM printed_products WHERE price < 50.00;
SELECT product_name, manufacturer, price FROM printed_products ORDER BY price ASC;
SELECT * FROM user_feedback WHERE rating > 4.5 ORDER BY user_id ASC;
SELECT user_id, product_id, rating FROM user_feedback WHERE product_id = 100 ORDER BY rating DESC;
SELECT user_id, MAX(rating) AS highest_rating FROM user_feedback GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT p.product_name, p.price, u.rating FROM printed_products p JOIN user_feedback u ON p.product_id = u.product_id WHERE u.rating > 4;
SELECT u.user_id, COUNT(p.product_id) AS purchased_products FROM printed_products p LEFT JOIN user_feedback u ON u.product_id = p.product_id GROUP BY u.user_id ORDER BY purchased_products DESC;
SELECT * FROM UserFeedback ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT product_id, rating FROM UserFeedback WHERE rating > 4;
SELECT feedback FROM UserFeedback WHERE LENGTH(feedback) > 50;
SELECT product_id, product_name, manufacturer, price FROM Product ORDER BY price ASC;
SELECT product_id, print_technology, color_options FROM PrintType WHERE color_options >= 4;
SELECT user_id, AVG(rating) as average_rating FROM UserFeedback GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY user_id ASC

SELECT product_name, manufacturer, COUNT(*) as total_feedbacks FROM Product JOIN UserFeedback ON Product.product_id = UserFeedback.product_id GROUP BY product_name, manufacturer ORDER BY total_feedbacks DESC
SELECT product_name, manufacturer, MAX(price) as max_price FROM Product WHERE price > 100 GROUP BY product_name, manufacturer ORDER BY max_price DESC
SELECT product_name, material, color_options FROM Product JOIN PrintType ON Product.product_id = PrintType.product_id WHERE color_options >= 10 ORDER BY product_name ASC
SELECT product_name, manufacturer, rating FROM Product JOIN UserFeedback ON Product.product_id = UserFeedback.product_id WHERE rating >= 4.5 ORDER BY product_name DESC
SELECT * FROM users;
SELECT user_id, username, email, created_at FROM users ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT product_name, price FROM products WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY price ASC;
SELECT feedback_id, rating, review FROM feedback WHERE rating = 5;
SELECT * FROM categories ORDER BY category_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM users WHERE email = 'john.doe@example.com';
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM users WHERE created_at BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2022-01-01';
SELECT product_id, product_name, price FROM products WHERE price > 100.00 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT feedback_id, user_id, product_id, rating, review FROM feedback WHERE rating = 5 AND review IS NOT NULL ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT category_id, category_name FROM categories ORDER BY category_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM UserFeedback;
SELECT user_id, rating FROM UserFeedback WHERE product_id = 1;
SELECT product_name, manufacturer, price FROM Product ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT username, email FROM User WHERE username LIKE 'j%';
SELECT user_id, product_id, rating_value FROM Rating WHERE rating_value > 3 ORDER BY rating_value DESC, user_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM UserFeedback JOIN User ON UserFeedback.user_id = User.user_id WHERE rating > 3;
SELECT product_name, manufacturer, price FROM Product WHERE price BETWEEN 50 AND 100 ORDER BY manufacturer ASC;
SELECT feedback_id, rating, feedback_text FROM UserFeedback ORDER BY rating DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT u.username, p.product_name, r.rating_value FROM User u INNER JOIN Rating r ON u.user_id = r.user_id INNER JOIN Product p ON r.product_id = p.product_id;
SELECT category_name, COUNT(DISTINCT product_id) AS number_of_products FROM Category JOIN Product ON Category.category_id = Product.product_id GROUP BY category_name HAVING number_of_products > 3;
